# Introduction to the Large Census Data 
## Overview 
*  How to access large census dataset 
*  How to choose large census dataset 

### How to access a large census dataset 
One of the good ways is using [IPUMS](https://www.ipums.org/), which allows you customize the tables the variables you need easily. 

Another way is to use API, which allows you to retrieve the data directly to R. 
You can setup your first API call here. 
